Delivery of the current version of the Functional Specification and Documentation of those parts of the Application to which the Patch relates, and if it is expedient for resolving the Incident (s), these parts can also be delivered in the next Upgrade
Successful verification of the resolution of the Incident (s) included in the Patch, where the Patch may not report any Incidents
If the Patch has not resolved all Incidents included in it, it is up to the Client to decide whether to mark the Acceptance Procedure as successful.
